abstract: Intel’s performance in the third quarter, analysts say, suggests that economic prospects are brightening.
snippet: Intel’s performance in the third quarter, analysts say, suggests that economic prospects are brightening.
lead_paragraph: Intel, the world’s largest semiconductor maker, offered further evidence on Tuesday that the global economy was indeed on the mend.

headline.main: Intel’s Profit and Revenue Top Forecast
headline.print_headline: Intel Profit Beats Forecast, Raising Tech Sector Hopes
